rComments: This class is BORING!!!  Sussman talks and talks forever about nothing and the TAs are very unhelpful also. He is not easy on the eyes or ears!  You do not need to attend the lecture becuase Sussman does not even know what he is talking about!  BEWARE OF THIS CLASS...IT IS HORRIBLE AND BORING!!!

SO BORING! Takes four lectures to say something that could have been said in 5 minutes.  He Always goes over the 50 minutes.  He has no clue how to come down to a student's level.  Don't take his class.  Take the Phil 105 with all discussions, I heard it was SO easy.

this is the most boring class of my life. i have no idea what i'm doing, and the final looks to be impossible. luckily, it's only 15% of the final grade. additionally, my TA was in his first year and could barely hold the class, let alone explain what sussman was saying!

This class is so boring, Sussman could go talk and talk forever ... just listening to himself speak makes him happy. Good thing he has good TA's to explain everything in discussion!!!! Not a difficult class but not a blow off either.

I thought this class was going to be different than it actually is.  The lectures are boring and usually pointless to go.  The readings are absolutely horrible and ambiguous.  Sussman rambless all lecture and you never really know what he's talking about.  You can still get a good grade as long as you do well on the 3 papers, each worth 25%.
my head hurts in that class
Lectures the whole period in an almost monotone voice so many fell asleep... don't really need to go to lectures... He could listen to himself for hours. Uses funny examples though, not too hard

He was a alright teacher.  The class materical was intersting and he explained it well.  The worst part of the class were the essays because they are graded hard.  In order to get an A on the esasy, you have to create a new theory.
